{"tid":2124123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會聯署促關美駐港領館","createTime":"2020-07-25T07:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T08:31:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"962d33ad85910ed03ffa239d0b192102010b99c8","tid":2124123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:23:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/TGHPIRO2WUYZ4XHAM7TE45TOGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FTGHPIRO2WUYZ4XHAM7TE45TOGQ%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=0d0425ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FTGHPIRO2WUYZ4XHAM7TE45TOGQ%2F&h=774a9948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/TGHPIRO2WUYZ4XHAM7TE45TOGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n工聯會聯署促關美駐港領館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YPvKr6Km_lHi046wpTMsrPy9brY=/472x170/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4PTEGY7HBWOTSDIOLKOMJEZBS4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYPvKr6Km_lHi046wpTMsrPy9brY%3D%2F472x170%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4PTEGY7HBWOTSDIOLKOMJEZBS4.gif&h=c2d9de77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美互相下令對方的當地領事館關閉，要求「封館」的浪潮蔓延至香港，繼建制派立法會議員何君堯要求美國駐港總領事館關閉後，工聯會亦跟風，發起網上聯署（圖），請網民支持關閉美國駐港澳領事館，不過工聯會是利用美國公司Google，發起是次聯署，並用美國公司facebook發出帖文。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：現場聽演說 王丹：如宣佈冷戰開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用Google聯署 fb發帖<br />\n<br />\n工聯會昨日發起網上聯署，呼籲網民支持關閉美國駐港澳領事館，終止運作，並強烈譴責美國粗暴干預中國內政，堅決維護中國主權及安全：「工聯會認為應停止美國駐港澳總領事館運作，關閉煽動本地政治不穩的基地，讓香港恢復安寧。」<br />\n<br />\n工聯會批評美國日前要。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯前日到美領館外示威，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"adbb3d72bd1287eac3c66019d8393f37aace459e","tid":2124123,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197a9936f47cfdd8ee3ff3070e9677811c8ddae0","tid":2124123,"uid":295442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"黃Sir教路<br />\n香港closed 去台灣開噃！<br />\n承認台灣地位！<br />\n<br />\n工聯會白痴！"},{"pid":"2dd6bb479525a0e9fb671a29c49339c28ce82398","tid":2124123,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"民建聯搞到WW3喎<br />\n<br />\n工聯會正垃圾 幫唔到手"},{"pid":"80861ef0d850e91d2c757644b4a4514fbeab2a6b","tid":2124123,"uid":24104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"使唔使幫手簽名，加速攬炒？"},{"pid":"2efcd7f5f8648ec4b2f9fe5b0826dba2af0ae54f","tid":2124123,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a169c98f4c3e8b3c13e18ade3761e4a9a93e72a3","tid":2124123,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:31:49.000Z","msg":"佢關門大吉=佢要炸左香港,佢地係咪白痴連防護罩都唔要,依賴萬個子弟兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}